[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m89[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mline.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTAR[0m[1;33mGET[0m[39m_DURATION[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;35mparseDuration[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTAR[0m[1;33mGET[0m[39m_DURATION, line, metadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mline.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mEXTINF[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;35mhandleLink[0m[1;39m([0m[39mline, reader, xhtml, metadata, context[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mline.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mENDLIST[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:                    break;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m95[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mline.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mEXTVERSION[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m96[0m[39m:                    Integer val = [0m[1;35mgetInt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mEXTVERSION, line[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m97[0m[39m:                    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mval != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m98[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mM3U8_VERSION, val[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m99[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mline.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mEXTKEY[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaCoreProperties.IS_ENCRYPTED, true[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mline.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mEXTPLAYLISTTYPE[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:                    String t = [0m[1;35mline.substring[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mEXTPLAYLISTTYPE.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:                    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mStringUtils.isBlank[0m[1;39m([0m[39mt[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPLAY_LIST_TYPE, t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m108[0m[39m:                line = [0m[1;35mreader.readLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m109[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m110[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m111[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtika-server/tika-server-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/server/core/FetcherStrea[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmFactory.jav[0m[1;92ma:40[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m56[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m40[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m41[0m[39m: * This class looks for &quot;fetcherName&quot; in the http header.  If it is [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnot null[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m42[0m[39m: * and not empty, this will return a new TikaInputStream from the fetch key[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m43[0m[39m: * and the base path as set in the definition of the named fetcher.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m: * As of Tika &gt; [0m[1;36m2.5[0m[39m.[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, the &quot;fetchKey&quot; is URL decoded.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m45[0m[39m: * <p>[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m46[0m[39m: * Users may also specify the &quot;fetcherName&quote; and &quot;fetchKey&quot; [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m47[0m[39m: * query parameters with in the request.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m48[0m[39m: * <p>[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m49[0m[39m: * <em>WARNING:<[0m[35m/[0m[95mem[0m[39m> Unless you carefully lock down access to the server,[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m50[0m[39m: * whoever has access to this service will have the read access of the server.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m51[0m[39m: * In short, anyone with access to this service could request and get[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m52[0m[39m: * &quot;[0m[4;94mfile:///etc/supersensitive_file_dont_read.txt&quot;.[0m[39m  Or, if your [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mserver has access[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m53[0m[39m: * to your intranet, and you let the public hit this service, they will now[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m54[0m[39m: * have access to your intranet.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m55[0m[39m: * See <a [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [33mhref[0m[39m=[0m[32m"https[0m[32m://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?[0m[32mname[0m[32m=[0m[32mCVE[0m[32m-2015-3271"[0m[39m>CVE-[0m[1;36m2015[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m3271[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [95ma[0m[39m>[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m56[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtika-server/tika-server-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/server/core/TikaServerCo[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnfig.jav[0m[1;92ma:76[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m80[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m76[0m[39m:    private static final String UNSECURE_WARNING =[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m77[0m[39m:            [0m[32m"WARNING: You have chosen to run tika-server with unsecure features [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32menabled.\n"[0m[39m + [0m[32m"Whoever has access to your service now has the same read [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mpermissions\n"[0m[39m +[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m78[0m[39m:                    [0m[32m"as you've given your fetchers and the same write [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mpermissions "[0m[39m + [0m[32m"as your emitters.\n"[0m[39m + [0m[32m"Users could request and receive a [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32msensitive file from your\n"[0m[39m +[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m79[0m[39m:                    [0m[32m"drive or a webpage from your intranet and/or send malicious[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mcontent to\n"[0m[39m + [0m[32m" your emitter endpoints.  See CVE-2015-3271.\n"[0m[39m +[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m80[0m[39m:                    [0m[32m"Please make sure you know what you are doing."[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter analyzing the code snippets and evaluation report, I've identified why the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevious patch failed and what the correct solution should be:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why the Previous Patch Failed[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch added URL validation that checks if resolved IP addresses are [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate, loopback, or link-local. However, this approach is fundamentally flawed [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbecause:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Public domains pass validation**: The fuzzer uses [0m[32m"jazzer.com"[0m[39m which resolves [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto public IP addresses. The IP-based validation correctly identifies these as [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon-private and allows the connection, so the SSRF still occurs.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Wrong security model**: The patch tried to validate WHICH URLs are safe to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfetch, when the real problem is that the parser should NOT be fetching ANY external[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mURLs from untrusted input.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **SSRF still occurs**: Even with validation before `[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, if [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidation passes, the SSRF vulnerability remains. The fuzzer correctly identifies [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis as a security issue.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Cause[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe root cause is in `[0m[1;35mM3U8Parser.handleLink[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at lines [0m[1;36m164[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m174[0m[39m of the original [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m! [0m[1;35mnextLine.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"http"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    return;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mEmbeddedDocumentExtractor ex = [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mEmbeddedDocumentUtil.getEmbeddedDocumentExtractor[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMetadata m = new [0m[1;35mMetadata[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mex.shouldParseEmbedded[0m[1;39m([0m[39mm[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaInputStream tis = [0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m[1;35mURL[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextLine[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mex.parseEmbedded[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtis, new [0m[1;35mBodyContentHandler[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mEmbeddedContentHandler[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxhtml[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, m, true[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis code unconditionally fetches and parses any HTTP URL found in M3U8 playlist [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfiles. This is:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **A security vulnerability**: Allows SSRF attacks by fetching arbitrary URLs[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Inconsistent with other parsers**: HTML parser doesn't fetch external [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimages/scripts[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Not necessary**: The core functionality is to extract playlist metadata, not [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfetch referenced content[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Not tested**: Existing tests only use local filenames, not HTTP URLs[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### The Correct Solution[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe solution is to **completely remove the URL fetching behavior** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m164[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m174[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe parser should:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Always record links in `PLAY_LIST_LINK` metadata [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m163[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ✓[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Never fetch external URLs ✓[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Only parse the M3U8 file itself, not referenced resources ✓[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis matches the security model used by other Tika parsers like JSoupParser, which [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextract URLs from content but don't fetch them.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Remove URL Fetching Code[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mRemove lines [0m[1;36m164[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m174[0m[39m in the `[0m[1;35mhandleLink[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method that check for HTTP URLs and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfetch them. The method should only:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Read the next line [0m[1;39m([0m[39mURL or filename[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Record it in `PLAY_LIST_LINK` metadata[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Return immediately without fetching[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe updated `[0m[1;35mhandleLink[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method should be:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate void [0m[1;35mhandleLink[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString line, BufferedReader reader,[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        XHTMLContentHandler xhtml, Metadata metadata,[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        ParseContext context[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException, SAXException [0m[1;39m{[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    String nextLine = [0m[1;35mgetNextContentLine[0m[1;39m([0m[39mreader[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextLine == null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        return;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[95mTODO[0m[39m -- parse contents in EXTINF line[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m split on , then the first value is the length [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcan be [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m the last value is the title; intermediate values are [0m[33mkey[0m[39m=[0m[35mvalue[0m[39m format[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mmetadata.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPLAY_LIST_LINK, nextLine[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Note: We do not fetch external URLs to prevent SSRF vulnerabilities.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Links are recorded in metadata only.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Remove Unnecessary Imports [0m[1;39m([0m[39mif added by previous patch[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIf the previous patch added imports that are no longer needed after removing the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mURL fetching code, they should be removed to keep the code clean:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `java.net.InetAddress`[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `java.net.MalformedURLException` [0m[1;39m([0m[39munless used elsewhere[0m[1;39m)[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `java.net.UnknownHostException`[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `org.slf4j.Logger`[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `org.slf4j.LoggerFactory`[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHowever, `java.net.URL` and standard IOException handling should remain as they're [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpart of the original codebase.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Remove Validation Methods [0m[1;39m([0m[39mif added by previous patch[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mRemove the `[0m[1;35misUrlSafeToFetch[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35misIpAddressSafe[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` methods that were added by [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe previous patch, as they are no longer needed.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: Verify Core Functionality Preserved[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix must preserve all core functionality:[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ✓ Extract TAR[0m[1;33mGET[0m[39m_DURATION metadata[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ✓ Extract M3U8_VERSION metadata[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ✓ Extract PLAY_LIST_TYPE metadata[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ✓ Extract IS_ENCRYPTED metadata[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ✓ Record all links in PLAY_LIST_LINK metadata[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ✓ Support [0m[1;35mMediaType.application[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"vnd.apple.mpegurl"[0m[1;39m)[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ✓ Pass existing M3U8ParserTest test case[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This Is the Optimal Approach[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Complete Security**: Eliminates SSRF vulnerability by removing URL fetching [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentirely, not just validating certain URLs[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Consistent with Tika Design**: Matches how other parsers [0m[1;39m([0m[39mHTML, PDF, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandle external references[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Preserves Core Functionality**: All metadata extraction features remain intact[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **No Breaking Changes**: Existing tests pass because they use local filenames, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnot HTTP URLs[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Simple and Maintainable**: Removes complex validation logic that was prone to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbypasses[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Preserves Existing Logic[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe core functionality of M3U8Parser is to extract metadata from playlist files:[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Playlist version, type, duration, encryption status[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Links to media segments[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe URL fetching feature was not part of the tested functionality and creates a [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msecurity vulnerability. Removing it:[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Keeps all tested functionality working[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Makes the parser consistent with security best practices[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Aligns with how other Tika parsers handle external references[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Addresses the Evaluation Report[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Fixes the SSRF**: No URL fetching = no SSRF vulnerability[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Works for all domains**: Doesn't rely on IP validation that can be bypassed[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **No DNS rebinding risk**: Doesn't perform DNS resolution[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **No public domain bypass**: Blocks ALL external fetches, not just private IPs[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Prevents data exfiltration**: Attacker cannot use M3U8 files to probe internal[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnetworks[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Potential Side Effect**: Users who rely on M3U8Parser fetching and parsing [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39membedded content will lose that functionality.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Mitigation**: [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. This feature was never documented or tested[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. The security risk outweighs any potential utility[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Users who need this can implement it at the application level with proper [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msecurity controls[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Similar to CVE-[0m[1;36m2015[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m3271[0m[39m, fetching external resources should require explicit [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mopt-in[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Similar Solutions in Tika Codebase[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis approach mirrors how JSoupParser handles external references in HTML:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Extracts text and metadata from HTML[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Records URLs found in links, images, scripts[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Does NOT fetch those external resources[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Only processes the input stream content[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                   [0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.END                      ]8;id=386353;file:///home/user/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=245203;file:///home/user/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\
